title: 140. Q&AF: Imitation, Bitch Voice & The Bigger Picture
itunes:title: 140. Q&AF: Imitation, Bitch Voice & The Bigger Picture
description: When you imitate someone, you are stifling your gifts. On today’s Q&AF episode, Andy talks why blindly imitating someone is a bad long-term strategy, how to control your bitch voice to build your discipline and how to cast the vision of your big dreams and aspirations onto friends, family and your team.
